cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper discusses the use of deep networks for automatic annotation of camera trap data, which is a common application of computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep networks also falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the need for scalable solutions, which could involve information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) techniques.
